    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Validation results demonstrate CFD model predicts relative hemolysis index within acceptance tolerances across the full CPB operating envelope. The 6 non-assessed factors are consistent with MRL 2 scoping. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Note: aleatory variability in the hemolysis flow-sweep validation result was characterized qualitatively by the study team based on replicate scatter observations; a structured uncertainty quantification record was not formally linked to that result.",
